# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Aria Code — Environment Configuration
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Copy this file to .env and fill in the values you need.
# ALL keys are optional — Aria Code works fully offline with Ollama alone.
#
# Usage:
#   cp .env.example .env
#   # Edit .env with your keys
#   aria-code
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── Local LLM (Ollama) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Aria Code auto-detects Ollama at localhost:11434. Override here if needed.
# OLLAMA_URL=http://localhost:11434

# Preferred local model (auto-detected if not set)
# ARIA_MODEL=qwen2.5-coder:7b

# ── Cloud LLM Providers (optional) ───────────────────────────────────────────
# Aria Code falls back to Ollama if cloud keys are not provided.

# Anthropic Claude
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-your-key-here

# OpenAI / OpenAI-compatible
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-key-here

# DeepSeek
# DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=sk-your-key-here

# Google Gemini
# GEMINI_API_KEY=your-key-here

# Aliyun DashScope (通义千问)
# DASHSCOPE_API_KEY=sk-your-key-here

# Aria Cloud (Arthera hosted service)
# ARIA_API_KEY=sk-arthera-your-key-here
# ARIA_API_URL=https://arthera.finance/api/v2/ai

# ── Market Data APIs (optional, yfinance works without any key) ───────────────

# US / Global market data
# FINNHUB_API_KEY=your-key-here
# ALPHA_VANTAGE_API_KEY=your-key-here
# FMP_API_KEY=your-key-here               # Financial Modeling Prep
# TIINGO_API_KEY=your-key-here
# TWELVE_DATA_API_KEY=your-key-here
# POLYGON_API_KEY=your-key-here

# News
# NEWS_API_KEY=your-key-here
# MARKETAUX_API_KEY=your-key-here

# Search (for /search and web grounding)
# GOOGLE_SEARCH_API_KEY=your-key-here
# GOOGLE_SEARCH_ENGINE_ID=your-cx-id-here
# BRAVE_SEARCH_API_KEY=your-key-here

# Macroeconomics
# FRED_API_KEY=your-key-here

# SEC EDGAR (SEC requires a User-Agent string identifying you; no key needed)
# EDGAR_USER_AGENT=your-app-name your@email.com

# Paper trading
# ALPACA_API_KEY=your-key-here
# ALPACA_API_SECRET=your-key-here
# ALPACA_BASE_URL=https://paper-api.alpaca.markets

# Crypto
# COINGECKO_API_KEY=your-key-here
# COINBASE_API_KEY=your-key-here
# COINBASE_API_SECRET=your-key-here

# ── A-Share (China) Market Data ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# akshare is free and works without a key (included in requirements.txt)

# Tushare (better historical + fundamentals; requires free registration)
# TUSHARE_TOKEN=your-token-here

# Self-hosted Arthera QuantEngine (optional cloud backend)
# ARTHERA_CLOUD_URL=http://localhost:8000
# ARTHERA_DATA_URL=http://localhost:8002

# ── Behaviour ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Session data directory (default: ~/.arthera)
# ARTHERA_HOME=~/.arthera
